relay and in the anchor position, and Dressel made it his job to ensure that his teammates were properly jacked up for this race.\\u00c2 Dressel personally exhorted each of his teammates\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094Jack Alexy, Chris Guiliano and Armstrong\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094behind the blocks before the race.\", \"from\": 3009, \"to\": 3305, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The coaches\", \"from\": 3009, \"to\": 3020}, {\"ngram\": \"the finals relay\", \"from\": 3033, \"to\": 3049}, {\"ngram\": \"the anchor position\", \"from\": 3057, \"to\": 3076}, {\"ngram\": \"Dressel\", \"from\": 3082, \"to\": 3089}, {\"ngram\": \"his teammates\", \"from\": 3121, \"to\": 3134}, {\"ngram\": \"this race\", \"from\": 3163, \"to\": 3172}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 Dressel\", \"from\": 3173, \"to\": 3182}, {\"ngram\": \"Alexy\", \"from\": 3232, \"to\": 3237}, {\"ngram\": \"Chris Guiliano\", \"from\": 3239, \"to\": 3253}, {\"ngram\": \"the blocks\", \"from\": 3277, \"to\": 3287}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 3295, \"to\": 3303}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His intensity was visible, perhaps because he knew he needed Olympic newcomers Alexy and Guiliano to get the U.S. out fast.\", \"from\": 3306, \"to\": 3429, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His intensity\", \"from\": 3306, \"to\": 3319}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic newcomers Alexy\", \"from\": 3367, \"to\": 3390}, {\"ngram\": \"Guiliano\", \"from\": 3395, \"to\": 3403}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 3411, \"to\": 3419}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alexy, a 21-year-old from New Jersey who goes to school at Cal, is a towering talent who stands 6'8\\\".\", \"from\": 3431, \"to\": 3532, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3457, \"end\": 3467, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Jersey_Devils\", \"score\": 0.6850964884544879, \"rank\": 0.459620300619807, \"text\": \"New Jersey\", \"types\": [\"Q4498974\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Jersey_Devils\", \"dbpedia\": \"h