rt\", \"from\": 4484, \"to\": 4488}, {\"ngram\": \"a dream destination\", \"from\": 4504, \"to\": 4523}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Guiliano recalls his official visit to the school, when he was on a campus tour and his dad, Joe, was walking across the school grounds separately.\", \"from\": 4562, \"to\": 4709, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4655, \"end\": 4658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\", \"score\": 0.9999851537733531, \"rank\": 1.4844893276807838e-05, \"text\": \"Joe\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Guiliano\", \"from\": 4562, \"to\": 4570}, {\"ngram\": \"his official visit\", \"from\": 4579, \"to\": 4597}, {\"ngram\": \"the school\", \"from\": 4601, \"to\": 4611}, {\"ngram\": \"a campus tour\", \"from\": 4628, \"to\": 4641}, {\"ngram\": \"his dad\", \"from\": 4646, \"to\": 4653}, {\"ngram\": \"the school grounds\", \"from\": 4679, \"to\": 4697}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chris\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 tour happened to run into Joe, and Chris saw that his father had tears in his eyes.\", \"from\": 4710, \"to\": 4802, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4745, \"end\": 4748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\", \"score\": 0.9999851537733531, \"rank\": 1.4844893276807838e-05, \"text\": \"Joe\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chris\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 tour\", \"from\": 4710, \"to\": 4723}, {\"ngram\": \"Chris\", \"from\": 4754, \"to\": 4759}, {\"ngram\": \"his father\", \"from\": 4769, \"to\": 4779}, {\"ngram\": \"tears\", \"from\": 4784, \"to\": 4789}, {\"ngram\": \"his eyes\", \"from\": 4793, \"to\": 4801}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last year, when Notre Dame changed coaches and brought in Chris Lindauer, he tapped into Guiliano\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s talent and turned him into a rising star.\", \"from\": 4804, \"to\": 4947, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4868, \"end\": 4876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Wilhelm_Lindauer\", \"score\": 0.9999960834861056, \"rank\": 3.9002887384493046e-06, \"text\": \"Lindauer\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Wilhelm_Lindauer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Wilhelm_Lindauer\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Notre Dame\", \"from\": 4820, \"to\": 4830}, {\"ngram\": \"coaches\", \"from\": 4839, \"to\": 4846}, {\"ngram\": \"Guiliano\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 4893, \"to\": 4905}, {\"ngram\": \"talent\", \"from\": 4906, \"to\": 4912}, {\"ngram\": \"a rising star\", \"from\": 4933, \"to\": 4946}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Guiliano made the world championship team in 2023, then carried the confidence from that into a huge NCAA season.\", \"from\": 4948, \"to\": 5061, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5049, \"end\": 5053, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"score\": 0.9999945742421771, \"rank\": 5.425787606731269e-06, \"text\": \"NCAA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Guiliano\", \"from\": 4948, \"to\": 4956}, {\"ngram\": \"the world championship team\", \"from\": 4962, \"to\": 4989}, {\"ngram\": \"the confidence\", \"from\": 5012, \"to\": 5026}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He came to Olympic trials primed, and made the team in three events.\", \"from\": 5062, \"to\": 5130, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic trials\", \"from\": 5073, \"to\": 5087}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 5105, \"to\": 5113}, {\"ngram\": \"three events\", \"from\": 5117, \"to\": 5129}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But there isn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t much to prepare a guy for his first Olympic swim, an